\f0\b\fs26 Overview
\fs24 \
\

\f1\b0 This project is an implementation of the classic Rock, Paper, Scissors game written in Python. The user plays against the computer, which randomly selects its move each round. The programme validates user input as well as tracks game statistics and allows the player to play multiple rounds until they choose to exit.\
\
